    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1905-12-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1905-12-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="372"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d372">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Tejera</persName> to Señor
                            <persName type="to">Joubert</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, [<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" when="1905-12-19">undated</date>]. [<hi
                            rend="italic">Received December 29, 1905</hi>].</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">[Handed to Mr. Root December 30, 1905.]</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Joubert</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Congress will accept treaty amended according to cable to Mr. Root December
                        7.<note n="a" xml:id="d372fna">Printed, <ref target="#pg_409">p.
                        409</ref>.</note> Executive approves. Caceres arrived to-day.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Tejera.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
